title: 368. Andy & DJ CTI: FBI Agent Escorted From Headquarters, Federal Reserve To Launch New Instant Payment Service & Elon Musk’s Warning About Shift To Green Energy
itunes:title: 368. Andy & DJ CTI: FBI Agent Escorted From Headquarters, Federal Reserve To Launch New Instant Payment Service & Elon Musk’s Warning About Shift To Green Energy
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss the FBI agent who opened the investigation into Trump escorted from headquarters, the federal reserve set to launch a new instant payment service, and Elon Musk issuing a warning about the rapid shift to green energy.
